īs analysiert. So entsteht ein einzigartiges Bild muslimischer Weltdeutung und Daseinsbewältigung, dessen Grundzüge bis heute gültig sind.  aThe best way to behave in the cosmos, which according to the Islamic doctrine is constantly being created by Allah, is to renounce all selfish impulses and become friends with God. This volume analyzes what this means for both individual and society by looking at the writings of ʿAbd al-Wahhāb al-Shaʿrānī. It paints a unique picture of the Muslim worldview and method of coping with existence, the principles of which still apply today.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 4aLebensbewältigung. 4aMuslimische Gesellschaft. 4aSufismus. 4aÄgypten / 16. Jahrhundert.  a16th century Egypt.  aMuslim society.  alife.  asufism.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2023z9783111318820oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978311078903440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311078911940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110789119423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110789119/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2023  aZDB-23-DGGb2023